title: A song and dance with Stephen and James
text: When two of CBS's funniest talk show hosts get together there's bound to be hilarity - GUARANTEED! James Corden from the Late Late Show visits Stephen to take the bromance a step further by giving the Late Show audience members a little song and dance. Watch them strut their stuff to "Me and My Shadow".
